# Optional. Both default to a public Helius endpoint that serves Solana RPC
# and Light Photon. Override only to point the site at your own infrastructure.
# A Photon-capable RPC is required for the Lookup/Verify pages (they read
# compressed PDAs); the public api.mainnet-beta.solana.com fallback will NOT
# work for those reads.
#
# VITE_CC_VRF_RPC_URL=https://your-helius-or-triton-devnet-rpc/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
# VITE_CC_VRF_MAINNET_RPC_URL=https://your-helius-or-triton-mainnet-rpc/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
